006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.util.ObjectUtils;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.Nullable;
012
013public interface INamedModelInstanceAbsolute extends INamedModelInstance, IModelInstanceAbsolute {
014  @Override
015  default String getJsonName() {
016    @NonNull String retval;
017    if (getMaxOccurs() == -1 || getMaxOccurs() > 1) {
018      @NonNull String groupAsName = ObjectUtils.requireNonNull(getGroupAsName(),
019          ObjectUtils.notNull(String.format("null group-as name in instance '%s' on definition '%s' in '%s'",
020              this.getName(),
021              this.getContainingDefinition().getName(),
022              this.getContainingModule().getLocation())));
023      retval = groupAsName;
024    } else {
025      retval = getEffectiveName();
026    }
027    return retval;
028  }
029
030  @Override
031  @Nullable
032  default IFlagInstance getEffectiveJsonKey() {
033    return JsonGroupAsBehavior.KEYED.equals(getJsonGroupAsBehavior())
034        ? getJsonKey()
035        : null;
036  }
037
038  @Override
039  @Nullable
040  default IFlagInstance getJsonKey() {
041    return getDefinition().getJsonKey();
042  }
043}
